      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken meticulous care of it, and it's been garage-kept and pampered since day one. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here! It's truly a gem and ready for its next adventure with someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
