    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes six individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear 333 hp. The drivetrain consists of a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission feeding an M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. This collector-grade example boasts a pristine subframe with no fatigue, a documented VANOS overhaul, and recent rod bearing replacement. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, riding on staggered Style 67 forged wheels. Zero modifications; original cosmoline still visible on the undercarriage.",
      "price": 44500.0,
